level.heading: Legislative History of Law 17-219
level.text: Law 17-219, the "Fiscal Year 2009 Budget Support Act of 2008," was introduced in Council and assigned Bill No. 17-733. The Bill was adopted on first and second readings on May 6, 2008, and June 3, 2008, respectively. Signed by the Mayor on June 24, 2008, it was assigned Act No. 17-419 and transmitted to Congress for its review. D.C. Law 17-219 became effective on Aug. 16, 2008.
